message: Mr Kamwale is very sick. I will be accompanying him to the hospital for evaluation.
Thank you for the message. Nurse Ngalande will be available to meet you when you arrive. Please keep us updated.
We are travelling well and will arrive at 5 o'clock.
I have Mai Peterson here in need of transport. Please confirm receipt of this message and expected pickup time
We have received your message. Nurse Makere and the transport team will be over by 5pm
The transport team is on their way and should arrive by 5:15pm
Hi, do we have a meeting this week?
Yep, we're all set for Monday afternoon.
We need some more paracetomol, can you please send some?
Of course, I will send some with Charles tomorrow. Let me know when you get it.
Thank you, we got the delivery from Charles.
